{"tid":1802113,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"19年富臨、美心蝕到hihi，如果相同既事發生嚮中資就真係光復香港啦（商業上）","createTime":"2019-12-29T07:46:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-25T16:34:13.000Z","uid":304769,"like":159,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":59,"replies":[{"pid":"5d2df20a304ad10acacd97e3dc36939f4a856870","tid":1802113,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T07:46:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ymsGDBU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FymsGDBU.jpg&h=8e0c6c6c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">先紅後藍，光復香港<br />\n加速支爆，拯救世界</span></span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>想經濟攬炒必須以打擊中資企業為主，尤其國企。請記住支共每賺到一分一毫，就多一分一毫整子彈殺手足。</strong></span><br />\n經濟攬炒target：<br />\n1.切斷中國國企在香港經營獲得外匯收入的機會，以加速支爆。<br />\n2.令藍絲企業經營困難，&ldquo;統戰&rdquo;綠絲企業<br />\n舉例，呢個原則點樣用：<br />\n基於先紅後藍原則，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">銀行方面一定係先中銀後匯豐</span></strong><br />\n根據先紅後藍原則，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">應該先Pacific(華潤)後Starbucks（美心）</span></strong><br />\n基於先紅後藍原則，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>&ldquo;幫襯&rdquo;紅店力度不應該比藍店細。尤其各種隱性紅店係支共既重要回血劍</strong></span>。<br />\n記住，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>如果想經濟攬炒以及加速支爆，就要紅死藍貧，紅死是為了打擊支共呢個恐怖份子籌集資金。藍唔洗死，但要慘比其他綠絲睇，就係為左&ldquo;統戰&rdquo;綠絲，壯大黃色經濟圈。</strong></span>"},{"pid":"a6f452b470958053a2ea536201dfb1922b1669f8","tid":1802113,"uid":27664,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T07:50:17.000Z","msg":"搵咗咁多年錢轉蝕少少錢啫"},{"pid":"c5d5eecdba6f0acd9b023779beb46589431bb155","tid":1802113,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T07:51:48.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"54c384bb1baf1ce30b9ac18a8705c5b213f3bb1d","tid":1802113,"uid":214192,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T07:53:05.000Z","msg":"大大間華潤係附近<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1e3854ef53b30e46144a1c0bf58f1d477cadb5c","tid":18